Comment: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:36.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,next episode title: New Year

Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:12.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wished you were cute when you met Kurumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:17.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about why you want to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:00.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yoshida and Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither is Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not looking my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:29.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think I dare look either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:38.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They're stone steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:09.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know; I didn't even s-see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:19.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, they're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu, call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:26.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we change our meeting spot? Why are we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:57.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu says he's busy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to say hi to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:04.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go make our wishes for us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:15.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bailed on Sawako too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's not sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:31.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's sorry she can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:40.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I still haven't explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:44.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see; they're backing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot of time until midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:59.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're giving out sweet sake over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're finally walking next to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're headed for the sweet sake next. Sweet sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had plans with Shouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:03.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but I want some sweet sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's embarrassing the whole class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His parents look just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sawako and Kazehaya are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, they're headed straight for Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:36.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves Kazehaya; he's totally going to spot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you all come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have invited me, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Joe, who are you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the usual crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at home watching comedy and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, no one left to get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where's Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, I thought I just saw Kazehaya for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya said he couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be here if he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's holding my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with some hot chick too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing he's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:53.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano might like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want sweet sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shit, I might feel her boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The sparks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty warm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go have some sweet sake and chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate sweet sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sweet sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:44.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll warm you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:53.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two for the couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:25.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm actually happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he might be annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:45.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just thinking too much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever\N thought sweet sake tasted good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't like sweet sake before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:25.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to learn new things about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:31.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see your “first ever.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,To see something about him no one else has.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:53.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time coming to the New Year's Festival with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also the first time I ever bought a girl's phone strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time wearing a belly warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a hand warmer in the pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My belly's all warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's my d-dad's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.22,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:33.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have given him the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:38.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:45.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to have something I chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:49.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:05.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, have you chosen an e-mail address?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I send it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.98,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I send it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:17.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's my first time texting; i-it might take me a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,what I want to convey to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:50.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it, I have too much to convey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:54.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where or how to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:14:02.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish there was a way to tell him in a single word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:19.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of wish I'd asked you for your number back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even “sort of.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd forced it out of you if I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:50.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sawako.not.sadako.1231
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to three and back to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When's your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barely made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:51.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have given you something if I knew sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to learn new things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:12.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see some of your “first ever” experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:19.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is about the time that I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:26.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with me at the moment I turned sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:34.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,11:45 PM. Sixteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen minutes until the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of kid were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:53.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start from the top, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were born about this time, sixteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:11.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. It's just me asking. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:22.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen years ago, I was born weighing 6.6 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:26.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered preschool at four,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:29.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Sumire and Suzuran groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:35.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is when my older cousin used to call me a Zashiki Warashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want coke, Zashiki Warashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:49.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in Ume's group in grades one and two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about three and four?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five and six?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you in to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solo rope jumping, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solo rope jumping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:13.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tied an elastic rope to some chairs, and jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And solo volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And solo string figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspension bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:25.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solo speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast, so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm going to ruin the mood again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ruining New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.68,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:46.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, if I'd heard all that when we entered school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have thought you liked being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:57.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're having fun no matter what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you're good at finding fun things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun imagining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:11.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He thought that of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered middle school when I was twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:31.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In ninth grade I applied for Kitahoro High School, since it was nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:40.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then in the spring of my fifteenth year, I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“If only I could be like Kazehaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:55.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe then something will change for me too.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:23.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been the first step for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:38.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year was too different for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take too long to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:04.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the end of my year with Kazehaya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:08.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and my birthday I spent with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:14.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A new year was about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:36.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
